These notes are somewhat deprecated and need more details.
See the README for more current info on installation issues, particularly as regards platform-specific customizations.

SNAC has three dependencies:
1. libxml2
2. MPICH1 or 2
3. GSL (Gnu Scientific Library)

Building SNAC takes two steps:
1. ./configure.sh
2. make

See the manual for more details:
http://www.geodynamics.org/cig/software/packages/long/snac/snac.pdf

